WEBVTT

00:02:59.208 --> 00:03:02.351
but our collective sense
of dissatisfaction

00:03:02.375 --> 00:03:05.018
at an unacceptable status quo

00:03:05.042 --> 00:03:07.875
kept us focused on getting things done.

00:03:08.958 --> 00:03:12.434
Some of those women went on
to open small businesses,

00:03:12.458 --> 00:03:14.101
repaid their loans

00:03:14.125 --> 00:03:16.809
and allowed other mothers
and their children

00:03:16.833 --> 00:03:19.726
to have the same opportunity they did.

00:03:19.750 --> 00:03:22.559
And we, we kept on going.

00:03:22.583 --> 00:03:26.726
In 2004, we opened
an agricultural training center

00:03:26.750 --> 00:03:28.601
for ex-child soldiers,

00:03:28.625 --> 00:03:30.643
and when the war was behind us,